---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | MinimalBlog">
  <article class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About MinimalBlog</h1>
    
    <div class="mb-8">
      <img 
        src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1181467/pexels-photo-1181467.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2" 
        alt="Workspace with laptop and notebook" 
        class="w-full h-64 sm:h-80 md:h-96 object-cover rounded-xl"
      />
    </div>
    
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
      Welcome to MinimalBlog, a modern platform dedicated to sharing insights, tutorials, and perspectives on web development, design, and technology.
    </p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
    
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
      We believe in the power of knowledge sharing and continuous learning. Our mission is to provide clear, accessible, and practical content that helps developers and designers improve their skills and stay current with the rapidly evolving tech landscape.
    </p>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What We Cover</h2>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Web Development</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          From frontend frameworks to backend technologies, we explore best practices, tips, and tutorials for building modern web applications.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Design Trends</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          We analyze current design trends, UX principles, and creative approaches to crafting engaging digital experiences.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Performance Optimization</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          Learn techniques for optimizing web performance, improving load times, and creating lightning-fast user experiences.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Emerging Technologies</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          Stay informed about AI, machine learning, blockchain, and other technologies shaping the future of web development.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Join Our Community</h2>
    
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
      We're building a community of passionate developers and designers. Connect with us through:
    </p>
    
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
      <li class="mb-2">Our <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">newsletter</a> for weekly updates and exclusive content</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Comments on our articles to share your thoughts and experiences</li>
      <li class="mb-2">Social media where we share additional resources and engage with our audience</li>
      <li>Contributing your own articles and insights (coming soon)</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 italic">
      Thank you for being part of our journey. We're excited to continue learning and growing together!
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>